DOC.brief_summary: This study assess effect pre-workout dietary supplement .
DOC.detailed_description: The purpose study examine acute effect pre-workout dietary supplement standard dose one deliver 150 % standard dose energy metabolism , cardiovascular hemodynamics , blood metabolite mental focus .
DOC.criteria: Participants must apparently healthy male and/or female age 18 40 Participants must least 6 month immediate prior history resistance training include bench press leg press/squat Participants history treatment metabolic disease ( i.e. , diabetes ) , hypertension , hypotension , thyroid disease , arrhythmias and/or cardiovascular disease Participants currently use prescription medication Participants intolerant caffeine and/or natural stimulant Participants pregnant lactate woman Participants history smoking Participants drink excessively ( 12 drink per week )
